### quotations.requestExtension [POST /quotations.requestExtension]

Request an extension for a quotation. Only possible for expired quotations.

+ Request (application/json)

    + Attributes (object)
        + id: `d885e5d5-bacb-4607-bde9-abc4a04a901b` (string, required)
        + send_to: `info@teamleader.eu` (string, required)
        + send_copy_to: maria@teamleader.eu` (string, optional, nullable)
        + subject: `I missed the deadline' quotation` (string, required)
        + content: `Can you reopen this quotation, please?` (string, required)

+ Response 204
